OL,3,CSunak's former aide among 15 charged
OL,4,Cwith gambling offences over election
OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FFormer Tory MP Craig Williams is among
OL,8,F15 people facing charges under the
OL,9,FGambling Act, after an investigation
OL,10,Finto betting on the timing of the 2024
OL,11,Fgeneral election, as ITV News
OL,12,FPolitical Correspondent Harry Horton
OL,13,Freports.
OL,15,FRishi Sunak's former aide Craig
OL,16,FWilliams and 14 others have been
OL,17,Fcharged with gambling offences
OL,18,Ffollowing an investigation into bets
OL,19,Fplaced on the timing of the 2024
OL,20,Felection.
