OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FWilliams, a former Tory MP, was among
OL,8,Fa number of people linked to the
OL,9,FConservative Party reported to have
OL,10,Fmade bets on the election date, which
OL,11,Fwas called by then-prime minister
OL,12,FRishi Sunak.
OL,14,FLaura Saunders, who was Tory candidate
OL,15,Ffor Bristol North West at the election
OL,16,Fand is married to the party's campaign
OL,17,Fchief, has also been charged with the
OL,18,Fsame offence.
