OL,4,Cwith gambling offences over election
OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FThe investigation, which was started
OL,8,Fin June 2024, looked at specific
OL,9,Findividuals using confidential
OL,10,Finformation, specifically advanced
OL,11,Fknowledge of the proposed election
OL,12,Fdate, to gain an unfair advantage in
OL,13,Fthe betting markets.
OL,15,FThose charged with a criminal offence
OL,16,Funder Section 42 of the Gambling Act
OL,17,F2005 are:
OL,19,FThey are due to appear at Westminster
OL,20,FMagistrates Court at 10am on Friday
OL,21,FJune 13, 2025.
