OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FAmong others facing charges are
OL,8,FRussell George, the Senedd member for
OL,9,FMontgomeryshire, and Nick Mason, a
OL,10,Fformer chief data officer for the
OL,11,FConservative Party.
OL,13,FThe former Montgomeryshire MP admitted
OL,14,Fat the time to having a "flutter" on
OL,15,Fthe election date just days before it
OL,16,Fwas announced in May last year.
