OL,5,Cdate
OL,7,FDarren Millar, the leader of the Welsh
OL,8,FConservatives, said: "Having been
OL,9,Finformed that Russell George MS has
OL,10,Fbeen charged with gambling-related
OL,11,Foffences, I have taken the decision to
OL,12,Fsuspend him from the Welsh
OL,13,FConservative group in the Senedd.
OL,15,F"The suspension is a neutral act
OL,16,Fpending the outcome of the justice
OL,17,Fprocess.
OL,19,F"There will be no further comment at
OL,20,Fthis time."
