OL,7,FA Tory Party spokesman said: "The
OL,8,FConservative Party believes that those
OL,9,Fworking in politics must act with
OL,10,Fintegrity.
OL,12,F"Current members of staff who have
OL,13,Fbeen charged are being suspended with
OL,14,Fimmediate effect.
OL,16,F"These incidents took place in May
OL,17,Flast year. Our party is now under new
OL,18,Fleadership and we are co-operating
OL,19,Ffully with the Gambling Commission to
OL,20,Fensure that their investigation can
OL,21,Fconclude swiftly and transparently."
